Global Contactless Power Transfer (CPT) Market Insights
Contactless Power Transfer (CPT) Market size was valued at USD 5.02 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.86 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.30% from 2024 to 2030.

Contactless Power Transfer (CPT) Market Overview
The global Contactless Power Transfer (CPT) market has experienced significant growth and is expected to continue expanding at a rapid pace. The market size was valued at USD 3.1 billion in 2023 and is anticipated to reach USD 9.5 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 17.5% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by technological advancements in wireless power transfer solutions, increased demand for consumer electronics, and the growing adoption of electric vehicles (EVs). As industries increasingly shift toward energy-efficient and wireless charging technologies, the CPT market is poised for substantial development.

